             hiha 90x150 hiha: an “orthogonal” programming language

   I really, really do not like overcomplication, and so here will be hiha,
   an “orthogonal” language with no formal report and just a Pratt parser.

   This compiler is a work in progress. Coding began 6 April 2026.

   Do not expect development speed. The programmer is medically retired and
   disabled.

